Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,eye catch

Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to bring Yawara-san back!{no split} So please, just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Didja just say yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really gonna do it, Beanpole?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Matsuda-san asked me the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was prepared to do it even before she was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how far I'll go,\N but I'll definitely do everything I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know damn well where you're going.\N There's only one goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come back aiming for the Barcelona Olympics,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that's sure to get Yawara moving again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:15.15,thought,,0,0,0,,Fukuko-chan.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.90,thought,,0,0,0,,Root for your mama, Fukuko-chan.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:24.91,epTitle,,0,0,0,,{\bord0.3\be1\3c&H3548D5&\b1\pos(320,340)\c&H1929D0&}Don't Be Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.87,announcer,,0,0,0,,The all-powerful Honami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:31.58,announcer,,0,0,0,,Coming off the World Judo Championships,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.71,announcer,,0,0,0,,she dominates the 48 kg-and-unders at the Fukuoka Internationals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.17,announcer,,0,0,0,,She's really on a roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Honami, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You must feel that you've secured your ticket to the Barcelona Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Olympics? I suppose I will go if that's what you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, your exploits are overshadowing those of Inokuma Yawara,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and it even appears that you might surpass her winning streak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokuma Yawara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, I do believe she was once a factor. I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:14.09,note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}Sign: Morning Sports#
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Her deportment was very much like a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Miss Honami at yesterday's tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Expectations will be high when she competes in the Barcelona Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hmph! }Laugh while you still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Fuku-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mommy is leaving! Be a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's finally beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm! I have to give her milk in two hours, so I'll be back by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good girl for Daddy until Mama comes home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold! This is definitely December!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let a little cold weather get in the way of bringing Inokuma-san back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:35.91,note,,0,0,0,,Sign: Inokuma#
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiko-san, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiko-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So she was flabbergasted?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! How many days do you think it will take?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not take days. You might stir her stumps tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,However long it takes, it's only a matter of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so you started today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Inokuma-san was so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We really need you to bring Yawara-san back to judo. I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to give Fuku-chan her milk. I have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Matsuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.61,thought,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Fujiko-san!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to work, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiko-san, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried calling you all day yesterday, but I kept getting your answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to feed her milk every two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're so busy, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell? I'm training!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Training? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why. I'm aiming for Barcelona!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Barcelona? You're not—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can follow me if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait, we can't have you skipping work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start running even earlier tomorrow. See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb. I know you're the one pulling the strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I, a slimy bowl of natto? {when you eat that stuff, you pull strings}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say a blessed thing! Beanpole came up with the idea herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,More lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who’s lying? This is what she told me after going through the labors of childbirth:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"My next goal is Barcelona. I will fight with my life to get there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That courage, that insatiable spirit to take on a challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,has moved me so much it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to fall for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiko-san really has her hands full taking care of Fuku-chan right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't even get much sleep because she has to feed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get her involved over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Over me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddaya mean, "Over me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a scheme to make me take up judo again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get conceited, you blasted fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in Sam Hill would work themselves to the bone to get to the Olympics for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get such a—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get such a swelled head, willya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fujiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A-About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandpa said something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're caught, Fuku-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true! I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be. I want to see if I really can make it to the Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for it together, Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you don't want to play a match against Sayaka-san and your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, but look...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody is hoping and praying that you'll compete in the Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Master Jigoro wasn't the one who proposed this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Matsuda-san! It was all his idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really concerned about you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Matsuda-san really cares about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't matter to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokuma-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my daddy says so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He says if Kosaku marries me, he might take over the business one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosaku's also into that idea. He might quit {\i1}All Sports News{\i0\fscx130} {\r}real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.90,thought,,0,0,0,,Who does he think he is?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.32,thought,,0,0,0,,What is he thinking?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.32,thought,,0,0,0,,What's with him?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.36,thought,,0,0,0,,I don't even matter to him!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:04.41,thought,,0,0,0,,He's quitting the newspaper, isn't he?\N Then he's marrying Kuniko-san, isn't he?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:07.41,thought,,0,0,0,,I don't matter to him at all!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is {\i1}All Sports{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make trouble for Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not play judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Let's talk it over—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother me ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}not{\i0\fscx130} {\r}going to play judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.67,thought,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. She sounded serious on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! Inokuma-san will surely come back to judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You said Inokuma-san would come back if I started training for the Olympics!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But things are different now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, Yawara-san might really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Fujiko-san. You can stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm continuing with my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you brought it up, I never even thought about doing judo right after giving birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I've started training,\NI'm reminded of how much I love judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play judo with Inokuma-san again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Yawara-san is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, this time we're running for real! Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait! Fujiko-san! Fujiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.96,thought,,0,0,0,,Fujiko-san...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:13:00.30,thought,,0,0,0,,Yawara-san is right. I only created more trouble for you.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.49,thought,,0,0,0,,But... it was all for nothing.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:12.65,thought,,0,0,0,,No one can bring her back now.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:20.15,thought,,0,0,0,,She managed to keep playing judo while she sought a reunion with her dad.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:23.69,thought,,0,0,0,,But now she's found out that Kojiro-san is Honami Sayaka's coach.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.12,thought,,0,0,0,,Yawara-san means it this time.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make trouble for Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}not{\i0\fscx130} {\r}going to play judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.25,thought,,0,0,0,,Yawara-san...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.91,thought,,0,0,0,,is quitting judo.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.81,thought,,0,0,0,,And there goes my dream.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I've been so busy it makes you want to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your efforts are appreciated, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the next thing on my schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You have two appearances on television, a commercial,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and tonight you have a launch party for your new photo collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's been like this all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I wanted to spend Christmas Eve with you, Kazamatsuri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Why don't we spend a romantic Eve overseas as a prenuptial trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh yes, wh-what a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sayaka, I hope you're not forgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Comte Bernard, who took care of us in France, is visiting Japan on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to be his hostess while he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.27,thought,,0,0,0,,Whoo-hoo!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot. I can't very well neglect to welcome one of my father's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't spend Christmas Eve with you.\N Don't think badly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, please, that's far from the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga, order a new dress for the welcoming party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.84,thought,,0,0,0,,Shin-chan's lucky!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokuma-san, someone called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a guy, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But he hung up before I could get his name. That tells me something's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you having a fling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.11,thought,,0,0,0,,Matsuda-san!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:17.41,thought,,0,0,0,,Why? I thought you were quitting your job and marrying Kuniko-san!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:20.45,thought,,0,0,0,,I don't even matter to you anymore!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, {\i1}All Sports{\i0}—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please cut it out, Matsuda-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawara-chan? Is that you, Yawara-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where is Matsuda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda-san went back to Yamagata with Kuni-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, you should tell him that all of his recent articles are completely—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.95,thought,,0,0,0,,Matsuda-san went with Kuniko-san?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.87,thought,,0,0,0,,So he really is going to quit being a reporter.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here to cover the ski tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.18,note,,0,0,0,,Sign: Hotel Matsuda#
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you came all this way too. I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All Sports{\i0\fscx130} {\r}is number one when it comes to cruel treatment of workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how are you feeling, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're calling me "Father" and asking about my health? There's no need for all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I'm as fit as a fiddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the tough-guy act, and I promise that you'll kick the bucket soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosaku! Try to be more considerate to your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a crying shame. I've been getting the same kind of lip from Dragon Lady here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling "Dragon Lady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm shaking in my boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Father! You always say things you don't really mean, just like Kosaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty, I guess I'll go prepare dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie daisy. {the "official" spelling upsy daisy looks stupid}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Father, I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no need. Just make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to help too, Kosaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay put! You'd only get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Dad. I hafta put together my manuscript anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Father, I'm a pretty good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a few young women know how to make kinpira like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll make a good wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, Matsuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My judo broke up my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad left to go train because I threw him when I was five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's trained Sayaka-san and returned as my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no clue how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make trouble for Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}I am {\i1}not{\i0\fscx130} {\r}going to play judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosaku, do you want some persimmon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem rather down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad looks like he's shrunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He returned from the brink of death, so what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He may not move around as much as he used to,\N but at least he's mellowed out as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can come back and take over the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were a reporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting that job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting like such a damned fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But scarecrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you run off to Tokyo even though I was against it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When you left, didn't you say you'd become the best sports reporter in Japan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you just bluffing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were chasing after the strongest girl in the world! You're just going to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not entrusting my hotel to someone who quits halfway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd best finish what you started!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that, then give back the money I gave you for Yugoslavia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the drive you had back then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.51,note,,0,0,0,,Sign: Tsurukame Travel Shinbocho Branch#
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Inokuma-san, you have a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that guy who called earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, you're speaking to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamatsuri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since we spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My workload's been crushing me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Yawara-san, do you have something planned for Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I've secured a reservation at my favorite five-star restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also taken great pains to be available to spend Christmas Eve with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Yawara-san. Would you like to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my daddy says so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He says if Kosaku marries me, he might take over the business one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'll be glad to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Kosaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to leave so soon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least eat the kinpira gobo that I made! It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we got to meet your parents. We should stay longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:42.50,thought,,0,0,0,,Go get her, Kosaku.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:48.76,thought,,0,0,0,,Yawara-san.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:59.98,note,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be1}Sign:The Barcelona Olympics in {\c&H5C74FF&}5{\r} Days#
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawara, where the heck are you off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I was going out for Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You non-stop, year-round party girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how much trouble that attitude of yours is causing your fellow countrymen?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you talking about? That's none of my concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get back here! You're the biggest no-account girl yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.56,0:23:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Greatest Present Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be getting my Okuri Eri Jime if you don't watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.92,nextEp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\bord1\b1\be1\fs30\fscy100\3c&HEBE7D7&\c&HF5F2E3&\pos(454.429,259)}The Greatest\N Present Ever!
